<h2 class="title"><a href="/blog/luisnassif/para-entender-o-caso-eduardo-jorge">Para entender o caso Eduardo Jorge</a></h2>
    <span class="submitted">Enviado por luisnassif, seg, 21/06/2010 - 07:11</span>
    <!--<div class="taxonomy"><ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_10482 first"><a href="/categoria/tags-do-blog/coaf" rel="tag" title="">COAF</a></li>
